{"tid":380062,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[唔講咁多即刻駁嘴]老母話我杯咖啡唔抵飲","createTime":"2017-08-29T22:27:52.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-30T01:29:52.000Z","uid":84267,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d9bb81c13b06f4fa1b57c67124321d04d1d87af0","tid":380062,"uid":84267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T22:27:52.000Z","msg":"話說呢幾日我成家人去澳門玩. 咁我對賭錢就無乜興趣, 行下鋪頭食下野就算. <br />\n咁今日同家人一齊食完lunch之後就打算各有各路, 佢地有佢地賭錢, 我有我自己行. 臨走之前我老母問我打算做乜:<br />\n<br />\n老母 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : 你會去邊呀?<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : 我求其去pacific coffee買杯咖啡, 跟住就周圍行囉<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : 哇, pacific coffee既咖啡成40幾蚊杯, 好唔抵飲, 用錢之前諗諗啦<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : 咁你賭場D老虎機夠唔抵玩啦, 你又衝去玩?<br />\n<br />\n跟住我老母就嬲嬲豬唔出聲入左去賭場, 而家都仲未同我講野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20cc00b3d3313f18cccf84291ba80746683b9adb","tid":380062,"uid":84267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T22:28:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c728b2faf42418308d98cf19227cceb225fb505","tid":380062,"uid":84267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T22:32:54.000Z","msg":"唔撚明, 佢地買件四舊水既外套就諗成半日究竟買唔買, 但玩老虎機半個鐘輸二千幾就okay<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2d9d6b785c4421307c55c0531f6b1e733bda7d0","tid":380062,"uid":81598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T22:33:58.000Z","msg":"屌得岩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢地咪又係倒錢落海"},{"pid":"bb5e94dbb7db2bc85831faa5026c221233841f5c","tid":380062,"uid":84267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T22:38:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌得岩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢地咪又係倒錢落海</blockquote><br />\n都無屌, 駁下嘴姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢地平時用錢就精打細算, 但一入賭場就另一個standard<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89be47435684d598f9e01a6f01c8ca17f2cff723","tid":380062,"uid":84267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T23:07:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"949b744d6587eb32a21cad715a5926b49737da40","tid":380062,"uid":33031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T00:49:48.000Z","msg":"咁杯咖啡係用你錢買咪得囉<br />\n洗咩你老母講咩"},{"pid":"374b91a7527c2bb2490e8bf5aa6e501312e5f515","tid":380062,"uid":84267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T01:29:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁杯咖啡係用你錢買咪得囉<br />\n洗咩你老母講咩</blockquote><br />\n岩呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n(酒店錢佢請<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)"}]}